    "summary": "The user expresses feelings of depersonalization and profound emptiness, questioning the point of continuing to \"act\" as if they still exist. The assistant responds with poetic, somewhat repetitive language that validates the feeling of emptiness and the \"ghostly\" state of the user, while attempting to frame these feelings as a stage for eventual healing.",
